开启AI功能,"Enable AI Features"
开启后，在页面编辑界面和可视化编辑界面中将显示AI生成内容功能和AI生成配置功能。关闭后，这些AI相关功能将隐藏。,"When enabled, AI content generation and AI configuration generation features will be displayed in the page editing interface and visual editing interface. When disabled, these AI-related features will be hidden."
开启多语言功能,"Enable Multi-language Features"
开启后，在页面编辑界面中将显示多语言内容翻译功能，后端会提示未翻译的语言信息，可视化编辑界面中也会显示语言切换配置。关闭后，这些多语言相关功能将隐藏。,"When enabled, multi-language content translation features will be displayed in the page editing interface, the backend will prompt for untranslated language information, and the visual editing interface will also display language switching configuration. When disabled, these multi-language related features will be hidden."
